---
title: Cajun Spiced Chicken Rice with Roasted Sweet Potato, Peas and Soured Cream
description: Combining sweet potato, peas and layers of flavour from tomato, onion and garlic, this veg-packed Cajun Spiced Chicken Rice is a wholesome and hearty meal. Punchy and smoky with a spicy kick, Cajun spice mix ties this all together.
